    <entry>
      <title>如何搭建blog</title>
      <link href="/2020/07/04/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BAblog/"/>
      <url>/2020/07/04/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BAblog/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>本文主要介绍如何零基础搭建blog,并使用hexo框架实现，即本blog使用的框架<br>+<a id="more"></a></p><h1 id="搭建blog"><a href="#搭建blog" class="headerlink" title="搭建blog"></a>搭建blog</h1><h2 id="框架认识"><a href="#框架认识" class="headerlink" title="框架认识"></a>框架认识</h2><p><img src="https://picgo-w.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20200703180021375.png" alt="image-20200703180021375"></p><h2 id="HEXO"><a href="#HEXO" class="headerlink" title="HEXO"></a>HEXO</h2><p>配置：</p><p>node.js</p><p>hexo</p><p>部署到GitHub</p><h3 id="配置node-js"><a href="#配置node-js" class="headerlink" title="配置node.js"></a>配置node.js</h3><p>安装epel工具包</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum info epel-release</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装node.js</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum install nodejs</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://picgo-w.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20200703185429661.png" alt="image-20200703185429661"></p><h3 id="安装Hexo"><a href="#安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装Hexo"></a>安装Hexo</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://picgo-w.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20200703190310513.png" alt="image-20200703190310513"></p><p>如果下载不了可以换成镜像</p><p>安装淘宝镜像源 </p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g cnpm --registry&#x3D;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;registry.npm.taobao.org</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>我在使用镜像安装的时候出现问题WARN Failed to install dependencies. Please run ‘npm install’ manually!</p><p>所以我直接使用的npm</p><h3 id="配置hexo"><a href="#配置hexo" class="headerlink" title="配置hexo"></a>配置hexo</h3><p>创建文件夹   用于存储blog0的各种文件</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkdir blog0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>进入创建的文件夹</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd blog0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>初始化hexo</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://picgo-w.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20200703193208534.png" alt="image-20200703193208534"></p><p>在文件夹里生成了如下文件</p><p><img src="https://picgo-w.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20200703193437235.png" alt="image-20200703193437235"></p><h3 id="启动hexo"><a href="#启动hexo" class="headerlink" title="启动hexo"></a>启动hexo</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo start</span><br><span class="line">或者</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://picgo-w.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20200704154037179.png" alt="image-20200704154037179"></p><p>初始化界面</p><p><img src="https://picgo-w.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20200704153955805.png" alt="image-20200704153955805"></p><h3 id="部署到GitHub"><a href="#部署到GitHub" class="headerlink" title="部署到GitHub"></a>部署到GitHub</h3><p>打开GitHub，并登录账号</p><p><a href="https://github.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/</a></p><p>创建一个repository</p><p>注：名字必须时账号名+.github.io</p><p><img src="https://picgo-w.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20200704154902227.png" alt="image-20200704154902227"></p><p>在本地blog0的文件夹内安装插件</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install --save hexo-deployer-git</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;下载不了使用cnpm,即刚刚安装的镜像</span><br><span class="line">cnpm install --save hexo-deployer-git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>设置config文件</p><p><img src="https://picgo-w.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20200704155901634.png" alt="image-20200704155901634"></p><p>打开该文件</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim _config.yml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在该文档末修改</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">type: git</span><br><span class="line">repo: 刚刚创建的网址</span><br><span class="line">branch： master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://picgo-w.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20200704160405522.png" alt="image-20200704160405522"></p><p>保存退出</p><p>部署到远端</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo deploy</span><br><span class="line">或者</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>部署成功！！！</p><p><img src="https://picgo-w.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20200704161653371.png" alt="image-20200704161653371"></p><h3 id="更改主题"><a href="#更改主题" class="headerlink" title="更改主题"></a>更改主题</h3><p><a href="https://hexo.io/themes/官网有超多主题" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://hexo.io/themes/官网有超多主题</a></p><p>或者<a href="https://cn.bing.com/搜索hexo主题" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://cn.bing.com/搜索hexo主题</a></p><p>这里我使用butterfly</p><p>文档地址：<a href="https://demo.jerryc.me/posts/21cfbf15/#測試版" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://demo.jerryc.me</a></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone -b master https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;jerryc127&#x2F;hexo-theme-butterfly.git themes&#x2F;butterfly</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>更改配置文件config</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">theme: butterfly</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后部署到远端</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
